:R-HSA-428643  a            obo:GO_0008150 , owl:NamedIndividual ;
        rdfs:comment        "The SLC17 gene family encode proteins which are organic anion transporters. There are three distinct subfamilies within SLC17; vesicular glutamate transporters (VGLUT1-3 encoded by SLC17A7,6 and 8), type I Na+-coupled phosphate co-transporters (encoded by SLC17A1-4) and a proton-coupled sialic acid co-transporter (encoded by SLC17A5) (Reimer RJ and Edwards RH, 2004).<br><br>Two members of the SLC5 gene family encode carboxylate transporters, SMCT1 and SMCT2 (Ganapathy V et al, 2008)." ;
        rdfs:label          "Organic anion transport by SLC5/17/25 transporters" ;
        dc:contributor      "Authored: Jassal, Bijay, 2009-07-06" , "Reviewed: D'Eustachio, Peter, 2024-02-19" , "Reviewed: D'Eustachio, Peter, 2025-08-12" , "Reviewed: He, L, 2009-08-24" , "Edited: Jassal, Bijay, 2009-07-06" , "GOC:reactome_curators" ;
        dc:date             "2026-06-29" ;
        pav:providedBy      "https://reactome.org" ;
        oboInOwl:hasDbXref  "R-HSA-428643" ;
        skos:narrower       <http://model.geneontology.org/R-HSA-9955298/R-HSA-9955298> ;
        skos:note           "org.biopax.paxtools.model.level3.Pathway" .

